sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.win32.coff

Interface DebugTypes


  • public interface DebugTypes
    Constants indicating debug information types in the DebugDirectory. (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)

        static final int IMAGE_DEBUG_TYPE_COFF

      • IMAGE_DEBUG_TYPE_FPO

        static final int IMAGE_DEBUG_TYPE_FPO
        Frame Pointer Omission (FPO) information. This information tells the debugger how to interpret non-standard stack frames, which use the EBP register for a purpose other than as a frame pointer.
